A similar metric is the expected cost (EC)
We define the dynamic EC \[ \normalsize\require{color}\begin{split}
    \begin{split}
    \text{EC}_c\big(\pi_i(s\mid t),&D_i(t,s)\big) = c\mathbf{1}\{\pi_i(s\mid t)\geq c\} (1-D_i(t,s))\\
    &+(1-c)\mathbf{1}\{\pi_i(s\mid t)&lt; c\}D_i(t,s)
\end{split}
\end{split} \]




